data.description: 3-bed home in the heart of town with great views to captivate your senses. Home has a large, fully fenced and landscaped .45-acre lot, an additional .034-acre parcel adjacent to the property is included. Inside has been thoughtfully updated; the kitchen has brand-new appliances, fresh paint on the interior and exterior, new Carrier heat pump/AC unit & water heater, heat tape in the gutters, and all-new LVP flooring graces the entire home. The fireplace is the perfect final touch. An abundance of storage solutions thoughtfully integrated throughout. The expansive 1,500 square feet of garage and basement space is a treasure trove for hobbies, projects, or storage needs. Potential VA assumable loan @ 3.25%.
